maven


build tool


1.we can install and uninstall certain packages and dependenices using some reference file

java---maven Ant or gradle

dotnet----Msbuild Visualstudio

python ----PIP

Nodejs----NPM

dart----programming language for flutter
flutter----same code mobile web and ios


2. it will also compile the source code

syntax errors-----it will identify the systax errors in compile stage

3.tesings----unit tesings


maven----unit testing and integration testing

unit testing----small part of application
integrating testing----all


java----pom.xml ----project object model

it is developed by developer


what is maven build life cycle


JDK ---Java development Kit

apt install maven -y-----jdk21

JDK----maven---Java applications compile


mvn validate-----configuration check---pom.xml---it will check project structure
mvn compile-----syntax errors----it will identify the syntax errors
mvn test--------unit tesing----some unit test cases will run
mvn package-----artifact----target floder----it will develop one artifact and artifact is nothing but war or jar 
mvn verify------integration testing---all parts of application will test in this stage
mvn install------local system project----.m2


